IBM has released a PDSE Monitor capability that is documented in
this url (created by tinyurl.com) https://tinyurl.com/y4lfwhry

From the document:

The PDSE monitor proactively detect PDSE resource exception issues.
Such exception issues can include processing hangs, latch and lock
contention, and XCF communications issues. The monitor runs as a TCB
in the SMSPDSE or SMSPDSE1 address space. The monitor task executes
t predefined intervals and it reports on PDSE resources that are held
or longer than a predefined duration.
